reviews.text: Wonderful food quality with moderate price level. Highly recommended with you wanna try traditional Hong Kong breakfast.
lovely place
The food is good, a little expensive, but a good place for breakfast or lunch.
Every local know this place for excellent food and nice owner.
Superb baked porkchop rice and other delicious food offered here. Be reminded that the shop floor is quite limited so if take away is possible, do it.

result.name: 樂樂冰室

reviews.text: 老闆非常為客人的健康著想，所以選取的材料如雞蛋 ，鮮奶，等都是用非常新鮮的材料供應，焗飯面上，加上水牛車打芝士。非常香和好吃，特別推薦他們的午餐，及焗豬扒飯，焗肉醬意粉，都是首選。 天佑香港！
還可以，三文治剛烤出來要快吃。
不知所謂的主打焗豬扮飯一粒星都多左又貴
有舊式茶餐廳風味！
